  <description type="morphology">Plants 10–18 dm, thinly tomentose. Leaves: basal leaf blade 10–15 × 1.5–2.5 cm, tomentose abaxially, sparsely floccose or glabrous adaxially. Peduncles 0.3–0.8 cm. Involucres turbinate, 3–3.5 × 1.5–2.5 mm. Flowers 5–7 mm, including 0.5–1(–1.2) mm stipelike base. Achenes 4–4.5 mm. 2n = 40.</description>
